data.description: Discover your dream home in Slidell! This inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bath property offers comfort and convenience. The spacious living room, with its open-plan design, flows into a modern kitchen, equipped with stainless steel appliances and a cozy breakfast nook. Enjoy restful nights in the comfortable bedrooms, with a primary suite boasting a private bath. A sprawling patio with new deck boards and a 60' concrete bulkhead with your very own 25' boat lift for easy access to all that Eden Isles has to offer and is perfect for outdoor relaxation or entertainment. BONUS - two game rooms above the garage (not included in living sqft) that could serve as an office or home theater (or both). Located in a desirable Slidell neighborhood, you're close to I-10, shopping, and dining, in a community known for its welcoming atmosphere. This home is more than a property; it’s a canvas for your future memories!  Call for your own private showing today!
